<br />
    </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Strategy</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">This is just a fun deck so play it ant way you want. I play it like this <br />
Start hobbit start, grab gaffer and try running 2 sites every time.<br />
the shadow is easy discard as much as you can to try your best to kill off all characters other than frodo ( HE MUST NOT BE KILLED ) Do not try to win it is more fun just to annoy your opponent to the point where he realizes you are playing a fun deck. After all this is what the game is about.<br />
<br />
For those of you who do not own any of the rares just throw in <br />
4x Host of thousands<br />
4x Backstabber<br />
4x Scrabbler<br />
<br />
For the fellowship side just throw in aragorn and athelas&#39;s this should work out I play the deck with and without rares I even won two tournaments with it. One with the rares and one without the rares.<br />
<br />
I think that most people will find that by site 6 you are usually decked and that is the fun part.<br />
<br />
Next deck I post will be Elf&#39;s &quot;R&quot; Us<br />
<br />
Thanks for reading have fun with the deck  </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000"> </Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">DeckTech <BR> For the Players, By the Players  <BR>www.decktech.net </FONT></TD></TR></table> 
